    # "I drive over to Juliana's house and knock on her door."
    "Dirijo-me até à casa da Juliana e bato à porta."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20g.rpy:6
translate portuguese u20g_4fc89239:

    # "It's late and I hate to wake her, but I need to see her."
    "É tarde e detesto acordá-la, mas preciso de a ver."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20g.rpy:9
translate portuguese u20g_5ac21d19:

    # "Juliana's grandmother comes to the door, looking surprised."
    "A avó da Juliana vem à porta, com um ar surpreendido."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20g.rpy:10
translate portuguese u20g_12baa67b:

    # jg "Oh you're Juliana's friend... I'm sorry, I forgot your name."
    jg "Ah, és o amigo da Juliana... Desculpa, esqueci-me do teu nome."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20g.rpy:11
translate portuguese u20g_529f52b6:

    # pc "It's [pcname]."
    pc "É o [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20g.rpy:12
translate portuguese u20g_0a7b8aae:

    # jg "What happened to your hair, boy? You miss a barber appointment?"
    jg "O que aconteceu ao teu cabelo, rapaz? Faltaste à marcação no barbeiro?"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20g.rpy:13
translate portuguese u20g_84c963f6:

    # pc "I'm sorry. I know it's late, but can I see Juliana?"
    pc "Desculpa. Sei que é tarde, mas posso ver a Juliana?"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20g.rpy:14
translate portuguese u20g_975fcca2:

    # jg "Oh, it's okay. I was up watching Love Island. You know that show?"
    jg "Ah, tudo bem. Eu estava acordada a ver o Love Island. Conheces esse programa?"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20g.rpy:17
translate portuguese u20g_70d520dc:

    # jg "I just love all the drama with sexy people trying to get in each other's pants."
    jg "Adoro todo aquele drama com pessoas sensuais a tentarem meter-se nas calças umas das outras."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20g.rpy:18
translate portuguese u20g_5ab1c947:

    # jg "Anyway, come in. Yeah, you can go up to see Juliana."
    jg "De qualquer forma, entra. Sim, podes subir para ver a Juliana."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20g.rpy:19
translate portuguese u20g_60d8396d:

    # jg "I'll turn up the volume on the TV, so you two can have some privacy."
    jg "Vou aumentar o volume da televisão, para que vocês os dois possam ter alguma privacidade."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20g.rpy:20
translate portuguese u20g_c6880d17:

    # pc "Thanks!"
    pc "Obrigado!"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20g.rpy:24
translate portuguese u20g_ea76bd5b:

    # "I walk quietly up the stairs and into Juliana's room. She's in bed, sleeping."
    "Subo as escadas em silêncio e entro no quarto da Juliana. Ela está na cama, a dormir."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20g.rpy:27
translate portuguese u20g_a95bfc0c:

    # "Trying not to wake her immediately, I lie next to her and wrap her in my arms."
    "Tentando não a acordar imediatamente, deito-me ao lado dela e envolvo-a nos meus braços."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20g.rpy:30
translate portuguese u20g_c981bd85:

    # "She jolts awake and looks at me, shocked."
    "Ela acorda de sobressalto e olha para mim, chocada."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20g.rpy:31
translate portuguese u20g_c026970e:

    # bn "[pcname]? Is it really you?"
    bn "[pcname]? És mesmo tu?"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20g.rpy:32
translate portuguese u20g_7f340d6d:

    # pc "It's really me."
    pc "Sou mesmo eu."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20g.rpy:35
translate portuguese u20g_b5e336f8:

    # "She leans in and kisses me deeply, her lips soft and warm against mine."
    "Ela inclina-se e beija-me profundamente, os seus lábios macios e quentes contra os meus."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20g.rpy:36
translate portuguese u20g_df5fc180:

    # bn "Oh, I missed you so much."
    bn "Oh, senti tanto a tua falta."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20g.rpy:39
translate portuguese u20g_cfc15aa3:

    # bn "So everything was true? You really saw your dad?"
    bn "Então era tudo verdade? Viste mesmo o teu pai?"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20g.rpy:40
translate portuguese u20g_e5c0f2f9:

    # pc "Yeah, I did. It's all true. I'll tell you all about it tomorrow."
    pc "Sim, vi. É tudo verdade. Amanhã conto-te tudo."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20g.rpy:43
translate portuguese u20g_2b545022:

    # bn "I'm just glad you're back. I was so worried about you."
    bn "Só estou feliz por estares de volta. Estava tão preocupada contigo."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20g.rpy:44
translate portuguese u20g_98d08bed:

    # bn "You look and smell awful though."
    bn "Mas estás com um aspeto e um cheiro horríveis."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20g.rpy:47
translate portuguese u20g_4aea05d2:

    # bn "I'll go get the bathroom ready for you."
    bn "Vou preparar a casa de banho para ti."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20g.rpy:48
translate portuguese u20g_a3acbba5:

    # bn "If you're going to stay the night in my bed, you need to shower and shave."
    bn "Se vais passar a noite na minha cama, tens de tomar banho e fazer a barba."

